*Mesto* je dom za ljude. (The place is a home for people.)
U *mestu* stanuje 30 000 stanovnika. (In the place 30 000 inhabitants live.)
On je iz *mesta* koje je udaljeno samo 20 km. (He's from a place that's only 20 km away.)
Bila je jedinstvena prilika da se poseti to *mesto*. (It was a unique opportunity to visit that place.)
Naš *mesto* je dobro poznato po pticama. (Our place is well known for its birds.)
U *mestu* je bila velika gužva. (There was a great crowd in the place.)